# 23. Quy tắc tính tiền order

```text
order_details.subtotal = unit_price * quantity
```

```text
order_detail_toppings.subtotal = price_at_time * topping_quantity * order_detail.quantity
```

```text
order_details.topping_total = sum(order_detail_toppings.subtotal)
```

```text
order_details.total_price = order_details.subtotal + order_details.topping_total
```

```text
orders.subtotal = sum(order_details.total_price)
```

```text
orders.total_amount = orders.subtotal - discount_amount + tax_amount
```

Backend phải tự tính giá, không tin giá từ frontend gửi lên.
